      "body" : "thanks for adding description here & in `sync_send_with_ping`, but imo it could be clearer. offering a suggestion incase you agree this captures the mechanism better:\r\n\r\n\"Ensure the recipient node has run ProcessMessages for all previously sent p2p messages\"",
